quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  70,40,"Alla woondiri Hoore Makko ko Kanko woni jom Funnaangeeji e Hirnaangeeji naange e lewru e denndaangal koode wonde ko O kattanЙ—o."
  70,41,"MeЙ—en hattani wattirgol Й“e woЙ—Й“e goo, Й—oftotooЙ“e Allah, Men halka fii maЙ“Й“e kamЙ“e. Men siforaa ronkooЙ“e gaynude fii maЙ“Й“e, wattitira Й“e woЙ—Й“e goo si Men faandanike Й—um."
  70,42,"AccuЙ“e yo NulaaЙ—o, Й“e jumpa e meere e majjere ko woni e mun, Й“e fija e nguurndam maЙ“Й“e aduna Й—am haa Й“e hawroya e Г‘alaande Darngal nde Й“e kammbiranaa nden ka Alqur'aana."
  70,43,"Г‘alnde Й“e yaltirorta e gaburuuji Й—in heГұaare, wa si tawii hara ko kaaЖҙe sanamu Й“e adandirta."
  70,44,"Hara gite maЙ“Й“e no heli, koyeera no suddi Й“e. Ko nden woni Гұalaande nde Й“e kammbirananoo nden e aduna, nde Й“e ittaanoo yiila e mun."
  71,1,"Men imminii Nuuhu haa e yimЙ“e makko Й“en, fii noddugol Й“e jertina Й“e, ado lette muusuЙ—e arde e maЙ“Й“e, sabu ko Й“e woni e sirkannde kon Allah."
  71,2,"Nuuhu maakani yimЙ“e makko Й“en : ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, min ko mi jertinoowo on, Й“annginЙ—o jertinaango lette habbitiiЙ—i on, si tawii on tuubanaali Allah."
  71,3,"Jertinaango am ngon, ko wi'ugol on : rewee Allah tun, hara on kafidaali Mo e goЙ—Й—um goo, huliron Mo Й—oftagol yamiraaЙ—i Makko e woЙ—Й—itagol haЙ—aaЙ—i Makko, Й—oftoЙ—on lam e ko mi yamirta on kon."
  71,4,"Si on waЙ—ii Й—um, Allah haforanany on junuubi mon Й—i humondiraaЙ—i e haqqeeji jeyaaЙ“e Й“en, O juutina laje mofte mon Й—en haa e happu mo Allah anndi, nguurnon leydi fotde hiЙ—on ГұiiЙ“i e Й—um. Ko woni tun, maayde nden si hewtii, ngal nennetaake, si Й—on anndunoo Й—um, on tiiЙ—norayno gomЙ—ingol Allah, tuubun e sirku e majjere ko wonЙ—on e mun."
  71,5,"Nuuhu maaki : Joomi am, mi jokkindirii noddirgol yimЙ“e am Й“en e rewugol Ma e wootinЙ—ine, jemma e Гұalorma ko ewindii."
  71,6,"Kono noddaandu am ndun Й“eydaani Й“e, si wanaa dogugol wЙ—Й—itoo ko mi noddata Й“e e mun kon."
  71,7,"Tuma kala kadi nde mi noddi Й“e e ko Й“e haforantee junuubi : wano rewugol Ma An tun, Й—ofto Maa An e NulaaЙ—o Maa on, Й“e uddira noppi maЙ“Й“e Й—in kollin Й—in fii wata Й“e nanu, Й“e buumora comci maЙ“Й“e Й—in fii wata Й“e yi'am, Й“e duumii e sirkugol ngol, Й“e townitanii jaЙ“ugol noddaandu am ndun, mawnintinanoo ndu."
  71,8,"Refti Joomi am, mi noddirii Й“ee e kene."
  71,9,"Refti mi townanii Й“e hito ka noddugol, mi gunndii Й“e gunndagol, mi noddiri Й“e noone fow."
  71,10,"Mi wi*ani Й“e : ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, Й—aЙ“Й“iree Joomi mon tuubaneede, tawde O siforii wonnde Haforoowo junuubi kala tuubuЙ—o e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en."